>Anybody know if my '77 Westy is still on track to become smog exempt in CA in 2007? It's due this year; so would I have to get one last smog in 2007, or should this one be it?

Sorry. Arnie rolled back (AB2683) the rolling exemption (SB42). Only 75 and older are exempt and that will be the case next year and the year after that until the legislation changes again.

